column1: Baby Barnaby's////This is one of my favorite breakfast places! The atmosphere is so much fun. The food is typical breakfast food - nothing fancy
column2: but always good. Order some fresh juice!! There aren't many tables so you'll probably find a line. It's worth the wait. I've been here a couple of times and the wait hasn't ever been long
column3: but I'm sure they have peak hours. Head there and enjoy your breakfast!
